subject: Awards, Decorations and Honors
Martial Arts
lead_paragraph: The martial art of wushu provided the first of an onslaught of gold medals for China at the Asian Games in Guangzhou, with the host nation excelling in competitions ranging from weight lifting (two gold medals) to dance (five).
